      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GALENTO (7) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing third and beaten half a length (29.59) behind Trendy Art at Sandown. Can find winning form. SLICK IVAN (1) three runs back produced an exceptional 22.10 win over 390m at this track then has found the minor money in two runs since. Has the ability and looks a key chance. ASTON SUMMIT (5) was a winner two back but last start drifted back and wound up strongly to finish a 5.5 lengths third at this track (25.52). Hard to beat again. PAW GERTRUDE (8) placed last time (25.16) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing second and beaten 2.75 lengths. Has already won five times from this draw.",
